<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.10">
<l>āṟe ṉakkuniṉ pātamē caraṇākat tantoḻintā yuṉak kōr kaim</l>
<l>māṟu nāṉoṉ ṟilēṉeṉa tāviyu muṉatē</l>
<l>cēṟu koḷkarum pumperuñ cennellu malitaṇ cirīvara maṅkai</l>
<l>nāṟu pūntaṇ ṭuḻāymuṭi yāyteyva nāyakaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You ended up giving me just your feet as a refuge, as path. I am without</l>
<l>any [to give] in exchange, and my soul is yours,</l>
<l>you with a crown of cool tulsi in fragrant flowers from Cirīvaramaṅkai</l>
<l>where abound muddy sugarcane and large red paddy, leader of the gods.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
